      <title>Monarch 募集 47 亿美元机会信贷基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/monarch-closes-4-7-billion-fund-for-opportunistic-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[专门从事不良债务的资产管理公司 Monarch Alternative Capital 表示，已完成 47 亿美元机会信贷基金的募集，超过了 35 亿美元的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/monarch-closes-4-7-billion-fund-for-opportunistic-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 15:32:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
